WEBVTT

20:56.240 --> 20:57.460 line:80%
I'm fine.

20:58.190 --> 20:59.800 line:80%
It's all blood from other people.

20:59.800 --> 21:01.070 line:80%
Help him onto the bed.

21:02.520 --> 21:03.390 line:80%
Careful, careful.

21:03.170 --> 21:12.700 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

21:03.960 --> 21:05.390 line:80%
Slowly, slowly.
